Package com.hurence.logisland.annotation.behavior

  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    DynamicProperties
    Indicates that a component has more than one dynamic property
    DynamicProperty
    An annotation that may be placed on a ConfigurableComponent to indicate that it supports a dynamic property.
    ReadsAttribute
    Annotation that may be placed on a Processor indicating that this processor reads a specific Record attribute.
    ReadsAttributes
    Annotation that may be placed on a Processor indicating that this processor reads specific Record attributes.
    Stateful
    Annotation that may be placed on a Processor indicating that this processor maintain its state after a process call.
    WritesAttribute
    Annotation that may be placed on a Processor indicating that this processor writes/updates a specific Record attribute.
    WritesAttributes
    Annotation that may be placed on a Processor indicating that this processor writes/updates specific Record attributes.
